The paper deals with generating 3D point clouds, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of self-attention modules is a technique commonly used in deep learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the paper discusses semantic preservation, which is a topic related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
